HEADWORD: Propeptone
<hw>Pro*pep"tone</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>pro-</ets> + <ets>peptone</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol. Chem.)</fld>
<def>A product of gastric digestion intermediate between albumin and
peptone, identical with hemialbumose.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Proper</ent>⟦br⟧
